波音的董事會在2013年5月正式核准該公司的民航部門開始銷售777X<ref name=777xapproval>{{cite web |title=Boeing Board Gives Approval To Offer 777X |url=http://www.aviationweek.com/Article.aspx?id=/article-xml/awx_05_01_2013_p0-575533.xml |first=Guy |last=Norris |work=[[Aviation_Week_&_Space_Technology|Aviation Week & Space Technology]] |accessdate=July 1, 2013 |date=May 1, 2013 |archive-date=2013-05-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130509200913/http://www.aviationweek.com/Article.aspx?id=%2Farticle-xml%2Fawx_05_01_2013_p0-575533.xml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[漢莎航空|漢莎航空]]的董事會於2013年9月18日批准了訂購34架波音777-9X客機與25架的空中巴士A350，用來取代機隊中的A340與747-400客機。在當時，波音公司已經有意在2013年中正式推出777X<ref>{{cite web |title=Split Lufthansa widebody order includes firm 777X |url=http://www.flightglobal.com/news/articles/split-lufthansa-widebody-order-includes-firm-777x-390732/ |first=Michael |last=Gubisch |work=Flight Global |accessdate=September 19, 2013 |date=September 19, 2013 |archive-date=2016-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160102165415/https://www.flightglobal.com/news/articles/split-lufthansa-widebody-order-includes-firm-777x-390732/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=lh777>[http://boeing.mediaroom.com/2013-09-19-Boeing-Statement-on-Lufthansa-Selection-of-Boeing-777X-for-Future-Long-Haul-Fleet "Boeing Statement on Lufthansa Selection of Boeing 777X for Future Long-Haul Fleet"] {{Wayback|url=http://boeing.mediaroom.com/2013-09-19-Boeing-Statement-on-Lufthansa-Selection-of-Boeing-777X-for-Future-Long-Haul-Fleet |date=20170723115231 }}. Boeing, September 19, 2013.</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.flightglobal.com/fg-club/in-focus/lufthansa-widebody-order/ |title=Lufthansa widebody order |last=Gubisch |first=Michael |date=October 2013 |publisher=Flight Global |accessdate=September 12, 2014 |archive-date=2015-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150709042722/http://www.flightglobal.com/fg-club/in-focus/lufthansa-widebody-order/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同年的十月，波音公司宣布，777X的設計將由在美國的[[查尔斯顿_(南卡罗来纳州)|查爾斯頓]]、[[亨茨维尔_(亚拉巴马州)|亨茨維爾]]、[[長灘_(加利福尼亞州)|長堤市]]、[[費城|費城]]、[[圣路易斯_(密苏里州)|聖路易]]的團隊，與在[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]][[莫斯科|莫斯科]]的團隊一起負責開發<ref>{{cite web |title=Boeing spreads 777X design work to Charleston, Moscow, defence sites |url=http://www.flightglobal.com/news/articles/boeing-spreads-777x-design-work-to-charleston-moscow-defence-sites-392371/ |date=October 30, 2013 |work=Flight Global |accessdate=October 31, 2013 |archive-date=2016-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160102165415/https://www.flightglobal.com/news/articles/boeing-spreads-777x-design-work-to-charleston-moscow-defence-sites-392371/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

